<HEADLINE> World Cup Biathlon Results </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, December 11 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results of
a World Cup biathlon event on Thursday:
</P>
<P>
Men's 20-km individual
</P>
<P>
1. Sylfest Glimsdal, Norway, 49 minutes 19.0 seconds (one
