<HEADLINE> Thai Housing, Construction Fair Opens in Myanmar </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, December 11 (Xinhua) -- A housing and construction
exhibition sponsored by the TTF Co. Ltd. of Thailand was
inaugurated here today.
</P>
<P>
The four-day exhibition, being held in collaboration with the
Myanmar Ministry of Construction, is aimed at displaying
world-class housing complexes and exchanging construction
technology, according to the exhibition's sponsors.
</P>
