<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 11 (Xinhua) -- Sixty audio and video programs
on everything from astronomy, biology, the environment, and
agriculture to the military were given awards here today.
</P>
<P>
The biennial prize ceremony, sponsored by the China Association
for Science and Technology and the Press and Publication
Administration, was held to promote the development of Chinese
audio and video programs on science and technology.
</P>
