suddenly, and the pilots were forced to parachute after they
failed to fix the breakdown. This was the second Mig-21 to crash
this year. Since 1990, the Romanian Air Force has lost 25 military
planes of various kinds, among them 18 Migs. (Romania-Fighter
Crash)
