Evening News that it did not mean that the sanctions would not be
lifted in the first months of next year based on the
implementation of the Dayton Peace Agreement.
</P>
<P>
Lilic said that it was much more important to Yugoslavia that
the European Union (EU)'s Council of Ministers has renewed the
most favored nation trade status offered to Yugoslavia. He
believed the EU would not favor the United States' decision.
