<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, December 10 (Xinhua) -- Orlando Magic's Penny
Hardaway will be sidelined for eight to 10 weeks after undergoing
arthroscopic surgery for a small cartilage tear in his left knee
in Orlando, Florida.
