Liberal Party president Raul Daza. The party is affiliated with
the Lakas-NUCD in a coalition.
</P>
<P>
So far it is unknown whether de Villa would follow his
supporter's advice. He and seven other presidential aspirants of
the ruling party earlier agreed to support whoever President Ramos
picks up.
</P>
<P>
For his part, Ramos dismissed as mere "grumblings" the threat
of de Villa's supporters, advising them to talk to de Villa first.
